/** \`icon\` — CSS-only icon: a data-URI SVG rendered via mask-image on a currentColor box. Inherits text color and sizes with font-size (1em). data-icon selects the glyph from a curated Lucide (ISC) subset. Zero JavaScript, zero web requests. */
